pageContext.claim: “No matter how many witnesses you give the Democrats, no matter how much information is given, like the quickly produced Transcripts, it will NEVER be enough for them. They will always scream UNFAIR. The Impeachment Hoax is just another political CON JOB!”
pageContext.analysis: Trump refused to let witnesses testify in the Ukraine inquiry, but some career government employees or former government officials did so anyway. But some crucial witnesses never appeared for questioning.
